workflows.name: Fetch Dashboard Data
workflows.description:
On page load:
1. Set isStatsLoading to true
2. Fetch dashboard stats from API
3. Fetch revenue data for current period
4. Fetch recent bookings
5. Fetch vehicle status
6. Update all corresponding variables with fetched data
7. Set isStatsLoading to false
8. Handle any API errors appropriately
